menu "Simulator Support"
     depends on LINUX

config SIMWATERTANK
        boolean  "Select the Watertank Simulator"
	default n
	help
	This configuration enables the virtual devices for simulating a watertank.
        The Simulator support is depending of an existing working OpenPEARL environment.
	The OpenPEARL compiler must be working prior of selecting this option.
	
endmenu	
